hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 两束光产生的散射力（$v\approx0$ 时）为
$$F_+(z)=+\hbar k\,\frac{\Gamma}{2}\frac{s_0}{1+s_0+4\bigl(\frac{\Delta-\alpha z}{\Gamma}\bigr)^2},\quad
F_-(z)=-\hbar k\,\frac{\Gamma}{2}\frac{s_0}{1+s_0+4\bigl(\frac{\Delta+\alpha z}{\Gamma}\bigr)^2},$$
其中 $\alpha=\frac{g_J\mu_B b}{\hbar}$。合力为
$$F(z)=F_+(z)+F_-(z)
=\hbar k\,\frac{\Gamma}{2}s_0\Bigl[\frac{1}{1+s_0+4\bigl(\frac{\Delta-\alpha z}{\Gamma}\bigr)^2}
-\frac{1}{1+s_0+4\bigl(\frac{\Delta+\alpha z}{\Gamma}\bigr)^2}\Bigr].$$
2. 阱深 $U_{trap}$ 是将原子从 $0$ 移动到 $\infty$ 所做的功：
$$U_{trap}=-\int_0^\infty F(z)\,dz
=\hbar k\,\frac{\Gamma}{2}s_0\int_0^\infty\!
\Bigl[\frac{1}{1+s_0+4(\tfrac{\Delta+\alpha z}{\Gamma})^2}
-\frac{1}{1+s_0+4(\tfrac{\Delta-\alpha z}{\Gamma})^2}\Bigr]dz.$$
3. 换元 $u=\alpha z$，$dz=du/\alpha$，并令 $A=1+s_0$，$c=-\Delta>0$，$B=4/\Gamma^2$：
$$U_{trap}
=\frac{\hbar k\Gamma s_0}{2\alpha}\int_0^\infty\Bigl[\frac{1}{A+B(u+c)^2}
-\frac{1}{A+B(u-c)^2}\Bigr]du.$$
4. 合并并化简为单个积分：
$$U_{trap}
=\frac{\hbar k\Gamma s_0}{2\alpha}\Bigl[-\int_{-c}^c\frac{du}{A+Bu^2}\Bigr]
=\frac{\hbar k\Gamma s_0}{\alpha}\int_0^c\frac{du}{A+Bu^2}.$$
5. 计算反正切积分：
$$\int_0^c\frac{du}{A+Bu^2}
=\frac{1}{\sqrt{AB}}\arctan\!\Bigl(\frac{\sqrt{B}\,c}{\sqrt{A}}\Bigr)
=\frac{\Gamma}{2\sqrt{1+s_0}}\arctan\!\Bigl(\frac{-2\Delta}{\Gamma\sqrt{1+s_0}}\Bigr).$$
6. 代回 $\alpha=\frac{g_J\mu_B b}{\hbar}$：
$$U_{trap}
=\frac{\hbar k\Gamma s_0}{\frac{g_J\mu_B b}{\hbar}}
\;\frac{\Gamma}{2\sqrt{1+s_0}}\;
\arctan\!\Bigl(\frac{-2\Delta}{\Gamma\sqrt{1+s_0}}\Bigr)
=\frac{\hbar^2 k\Gamma^2 s_0}{2\,g_J\mu_B b\,\sqrt{1+s_0}}
\arctan\!\Bigl(\frac{-2\Delta}{\Gamma\sqrt{1+s_0}}\Bigr).$$
